(174, 1, '2013-12-06 23:14:00', '2013-12-07 04:14:00', '[smartslider2 slider="100015"]\r\n<h3>Welcome to another potentially never-ending discussion: <strong>Laptop or Desktop?</strong></h3>\r\nThis website is dedicated to compare and contrast the pros and cons of all personal computer systems. When we say "desktop," we categorically refer to all devices that are wired and cannot accompany us when are on the leave. A laptop represents the mobility notion and all devices such as tablets or cell phones that can travel with us belong to this category. Ready for the debate? Get registered and have your say. Agree or disagree with other postings, create your own threads, tell stories, be anecdotal or theoretical.\r\n<p class="webFont">Hey you, don''t sleep there. If you wonder what the heck is going on here, just create yet another dummy contributor account and copy &amp;paste some stuff. No one is going to read these dude, you can be impolite as much as you want.<br />\r\nThis web font is intended to demonstrate the style that wascustomised usingthe admin side, made possible by the theme CUSTOM COMMUNITY. This web font is called "Architect''s Daughter" and its CDN is Google.</p>', 'Home', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'home', '', '', '2013-12-09 23:57:22', '2013-12-10 04:57:22', '', 0, 'http://webforum.grifare.com/?page_id=174', 0, 'page', '', 0),
